    "## ðŸ“š Vegetation Index Fundamentals\n",
    "\n",
    "### Common Vegetation Indices\n",
    "\n",
    "| Index | Formula | Range | Description |\n",
    "|-------|---------|-------|-------------|\n",
    "| **NDVI** | `(NIR - Red) / (NIR + Red)` | -1 to 1 | Most common vegetation index |\n",
    "| **EVI** | `2.5 * (NIR - Red) / (NIR + 6*Red - 7.5*Blue + 1)` | -1 to 1 | Enhanced, atmospheric corrected |\n",
    "| **SAVI** | `(NIR - Red) / (NIR + Red + L) * (1 + L)` | -1 to 1 | Soil-adjusted (L=0.5) |\n",
    "| **NDWI** | `(Green - NIR) / (Green + NIR)` | -1 to 1 | Water detection |\n",
    "| **GNDVI** | `(NIR - Green) / (NIR + Green)` | -1 to 1 | Green-based vegetation |\n",
    "\n",
    "### Spectral Band Requirements\n",
    "```python\n",
    "# Typical satellite sensor band configurations\n",
    "BAND_CONFIGS = {\n",
    "    'landsat8': {\n",
    "        'blue': 2, 'green': 3, 'red': 4, 'nir': 5, 'swir1': 6, 'swir2': 7\n",
    "    },\n",
    "    'sentinel2': {\n",
    "        'blue': 2, 'green': 3, 'red': 4, 'nir': 8, 'swir1': 11, 'swir2': 12\n",
    "    },\n",
    "    'generic': {\n",
    "        'blue': 1, 'green': 2, 'red': 3, 'nir': 4\n",
    "    }\n",
    "}\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### Index Interpretation\n",
    "- **NDVI > 0.7**: Dense vegetation (forests)\n",
    "- **NDVI 0.4-0.7**: Moderate vegetation (grasslands, crops)\n",
    "- **NDVI 0.2-0.4**: Sparse vegetation\n",
    "- **NDVI < 0.2**: Non-vegetated (water, urban, bare soil)"
   ]
